---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About Fatawa Library</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="about-content">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Fatawa Library is a curated, scholarly archive of Islamic legal rulings (fatāwā)
        from senior, trusted scholars. We translate and present these rulings in clear,
        readable English while preserving the original Arabic source and full context.
      </p>

      <h2>Content Standards</h2>
      <p>
        Every fatwa includes the original source URL and is presented with its complete
        evidence. We do not edit or paraphrase rulings; we translate faithfully.
      </p>

      <h2>Scholars Included</h2>
      <p>
        Our current archive features rulings from Shaykh ʿAbd al‑ʿAzīz ibn Bāz,
        Shaykh Muḥammad ibn Ṣāliḥ al‑ʿUthaymīn, Shaykh Muḥammad Nāṣir al‑Dīn al‑Albānī,
        Shaykh Muqbil al‑Wādiʿī, and Shaykh Yaḥyā al‑Ḥajūrī. More scholars will be added
        over time.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The translations are provided for educational and research purposes.
        They are not a substitute for consulting a qualified scholar for personal
        religious guidance. Always refer to the original Arabic when in doubt.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact & Corrections</h2>
      <p>
        If you find an error or have a suggestion, please email us at
        <a href="mailto:fatawalib@example.com">fatawalib@example.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .about-header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-default);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .about-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-content p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-content a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .about-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>